Play this card as if it were a 40-HP Basic Colorless Pokemon. At any time during your turn, you may discard this card from play. This card can't retreat.
Put a Basic Pokemon from your opponent's discard pile onto their Bench.
Look at the top card of your deck. If that card is a Psychic Pokemon, put it in your hand. If it is not a Psychic Pokemon, put it on the bottom of your deck.
Put your Mew ex in the Active Spot into your hand.
During your opponent's next turn, all of your Pokemon take -10 damage from attacks from your opponent's Pokemon.
During this turn, the Retreat Cost of your Active Pokemon is 2 less.

retreat_cost__effect: Play this card as if it were a 40-HP Basic Colorless Pokemon. At any time during your turn, you may discard this card from play. This card can't retreat.
Play this card as if it were a 40-HP Basic Colorless Pokemon. At any time during your turn, you may discard this card from play. This card can't retreat.
Choose a Pokemon in your hand and switch it with a random Pokemon from your deck.
The Pokemon this card is attatched to gets +20 HP.
If the Pokemon this card is attatched to is in the Active Spot and is damaged by your opponent's Pokemon, do 20 damage to the attacking Pokemon.
At the end of each turn, if the Pokemon this card is attatched to is affected by any Special Conditions, it recovers from all of them, and discard this card.
Switch 1 of your opponent's Pokemon that has damage on it to the Active Spot.
Put 1 random Glameow, Stunky, or Croagunk from your deck to your hand.
During this turn, attacks used by your Garchomp or Togekiss do +50 damage to your opponent's Active Pokemon.
Choose 1 of your Electivire or Luxray. Attatch 2 Lightning Energy from your discard pile to that Pokemon.
Move an Energy from 1 of your Benched Pokemon to your Active Pokemon.
Your opponent shuffles their hand into their deck and draws a card for each of their remaining points needed to win.
